h4. Actor:
Administrator, Remittance User, Exchange House User.

h4. Description:
Name of the use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Disbursement sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Create* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Task"|guide:ShowRmsTaskActionService].
* Populate "Exchange House" List in drop-down.

h4. Pre-condition:
* [Exchange House must be created|guide:CreateRmsExchangeHouseActionService] from settings.

h4. Process:
* Get "Exchange House" list from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Populate "Exchange House" list in drop down.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

